name: Royal Belgian Institute of Natural Sciences Echinodermata Collection (Echinodermata)
description: The Royal Belgian Institute of Natural Sciences Echinodermatacollection contains 4275 digitisedspecimens over 403 taxa (mostly species). This dataset only contains the marinespecies of the collection.
